WEBVTT

00:00.203 --> 00:02.919
I was part of the plot to bomb
New York City.

00:03.039 --> 00:04.715
Please! If you testify...

00:04.835 --> 00:07.136
I refuse to continue
be a part of this...

00:07.138 --> 00:09.638
Now's not the time
to be stupid.

00:09.640 --> 00:11.507
I will not involve my
husband in my mistakes

00:11.509 --> 00:13.809
and you will not become
free of this jail.

00:13.811 --> 00:15.077
We've found the plantation

00:15.079 --> 00:16.277
to which your mother was sold.

00:16.280 --> 00:18.447
I personally will go
to the plantation

00:18.449 --> 00:21.350
and shepherd Sara's
mother to your door.

00:21.352 --> 00:24.787
You saved my life
when New York burnt.

00:24.789 --> 00:26.155
Now I saved yours.

00:26.157 --> 00:27.323
We're square.

00:27.325 --> 00:29.191
Detective Maguire.

00:29.193 --> 00:31.827
Shake the man's hand,
detective.

