42:10.359 --> 42:12.127
Well, I'd say we've got
a cholera outbreak

42:12.129 --> 42:13.228
on our hands.

42:13.230 --> 42:15.397
I'm trying to secure
the contract

42:15.399 --> 42:16.760
to build the city's
new aqueduct.

42:16.880 --> 42:19.367
This man is my only
viable competition.

42:19.369 --> 42:20.902
Come sit with daddy,
little monkey.

42:20.904 --> 42:22.204
Corcoran: It's hard
to tell, sometimes,

42:22.206 --> 42:24.139
but there is a difference

42:24.141 --> 42:26.341
between a man and an animal.

42:26.343 --> 42:28.410
We built a goddamn
train track to nowhere.

42:28.412 --> 42:30.579
How much is lost?

42:30.581 --> 42:31.947
You would hate to wind up
penniless, wouldn't you?

42:31.949 --> 42:34.516
Neglect sometimes
feeds anticipation.

42:34.518 --> 42:36.284
Ellen: I feel it
coming on

42:36.286 --> 42:44.286
like a storm about to break.

